about & contact

Insufficient Underground is a news outlet catering to the underground hip-hop community. Insufficient started in 2017 as a simple T-shirt idea, and now has grown into a hip-hop platform. One day I have hopes of having my own label, and pursuing a career in artist and repertoire. - Founder, Tucker Farner
